{"tid":511964,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利比里亞總統：雲加令我成功","createTime":"2017-12-28T03:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T05:34:05.000Z","uid":30768,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7b250e5bcef82b65bfea01d3be6d53ba0742790e","tid":511964,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"韋亞：雲格令我成功<br />\n<br />\n當時摩納哥主帥雲格，卻在種族主義的巔峰時期，向韋亞展示了愛與關懷，韋亞形容雲格「他如同父親一樣，把我當作兒子。」有一次，迷茫的韋亞厭倦了訓練，並告訴雲格自己很頭痛，惟雲格鼓勵道：「喬治，我知道這很辛苦，但你要努力。 我相信你的天份，你能夠成為世上最好球員之一。」韋亞回想當初，他感言：「在神以外，沒有雲格的話，我當年不可能成功。」"},{"pid":"9c88ccf5302b5d3574df7c5b79d23f034da995c9","tid":511964,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爺爺"},{"pid":"25f5576c642692819265428a43d4d8cfc96addf1","tid":511964,"uid":24524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa699877e1e4d1ee709fd9f07e54857c7f856cb","tid":511964,"uid":46642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:03:06.000Z","msg":"爺爺又然"},{"pid":"0e98a7fa55b4c164fe579924594c5ac25889737f","tid":511964,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:05:44.000Z","msg":"邊隻反雲狗比負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3adc4df5e45ed98cb65856f6bfaf013eb87b19db","tid":511964,"uid":84228,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:06:55.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺弟子：做總統<br />\n費蛇弟子：上弟婦"},{"pid":"14a3b0b1a7708f84559da08a4ef7039ea0407ec0","tid":511964,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04: